Program: Outlook
Title: The ‘Lion Mama’ who fought off three rapists
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt7c
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 31 Mar 2019
When Nokubonga Qampi was told that her daughter was being raped by three men, she took action. One attacker would end up dead, the others seriously injured. Nokubonga was faced with the prospect of prison, but then her story made her famous and she became a hero to many. They called her 'Lion Mama'. Presenter: Gavin Fischer Producer: Harry Graham Image: Nokubonga Qampi Credit: BBC Show less